eloper.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n150%;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" georgia\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Please <a href=\"https://techgenix.com/full-stack-developer/\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\">Click Here</a> for the details of how to become a full stack developer.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n150%;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" georgia\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Author</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n150%;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" georgia\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">Aklilu Mandefro, Gondar, Ethiopia<br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\n150%;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\r\nfont-family:\" georgia\",\"serif\";mso-fareast-font-family:\"times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" mso-bidi-font-family:\"times=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\"><br></span></p>', '63560400_1524778647.jpg', 'draft', NULL, NULL, '5');
